name: I Spend Time [Void of Meaning]
description:
This video piece is the opening statement of the "Void of Meaning" collection.

-

The pursuit of meaning is heavy, wearisome and bound to frustration. Refrain from it and you'll find rest.

- 

Full HD h264 video. Wheat flour over teflon. Digital manipulation. Characters made in Processing.

Feel free to contact me for a Pro Res Quality file.

'I Spend Time', 2022
